These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, 7up, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: hot-chocolate-polo, snowboarding, surfing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
2. the person drinking cola is not the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo##6
3. the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo##1
6. the person who's sport is hot-chocolate-polo is not the person drinking 7up##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola   | hot-chocolate    | milk    | 7up |
| Sport      | rugby | hot-chocolate-polo | surfing | snowboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta
There 4 different types of food: apple, watermelon, cabbage, lemon
1. the person eating apple is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
3. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person drinking fanta##5
4. the person drinking coffee is not the person eating watermelon##6
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | coffee  | hot-chocolate    | cola | fanta    |
| Food       | lemon | watermelon | cabbage  | apple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, iced-tea, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, social-worker, manager, designer
1. the person drinking cola is not the pilot##6
2. the social-worker is not the person drinking iced-tea##6
3. the manager is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
4. the social-worker is the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the social-worker##1
6. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
7. the pilot is on the far left or far right##3
8. the manager is somewhere to the left of the designer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | cola       | juice  | coffee  | iced-tea |
| Job        | manager | designer | social-worker | pilot  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rat, horse, mouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, ship, motorbike, roller
1. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
3. the person driving the roller is not the owner of the rat##6
4. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | rat | horse | mouse     | ferret |
| Transport   | ship     | motorbike    | boat | roller    |

