.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, jet-ski, train
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person driving the jet-ski##5
3. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
4. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person driving the train##6
5. the person driving the skateboard is not the person drinking water##6
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | water        | lemonade | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Transport   | train | skateboard | subway     | jet-ski   |

