.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, documentary, satire, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, british, spanish, argentine
1. the russian is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is not the british##6
3. the russian is on the far right##1
4. the british is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
5. the person watching satire movies is the person watching satire movies##1
6. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the russian##5
7. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
8. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
9. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | satire    | western  | comedy   |
| Nationality   | spanish  | argentine | british | russian |

