.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, romance, crime
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, electronic, classical, folk
1. the fan classical is on the left or right of the fan rock##3
2. the fan classical is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
3. the person watching animation movies is the fan electronic##1
4. the fan rock is on the left or right of the fan folk##3
5. the fan classical is on the far left##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is the fan rock##1
7. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the left of the fan rock##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | fantasy     | romance | animation |
| Music-Genre   | classical | rock | folk      | electronic         |

