.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, fisherman, accountant, bartender
1. the engineer is on the left of the fisherman##1
2. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the accountant##5
3. the bartender is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
6. the engineer is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not the bartender##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate  | water        | almond-milk      | fanta          |
| Job        | engineer | fisherman | bartender | accountant |

