.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, manager, software-developer, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, bus, van, jet-ski
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the bus is not the writer##6
3. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the van##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the software-developer##1
7. the police-officer is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
8. the manager is somewhere to the right of the writer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | police-officer  | software-developer | writer    | manager |
| Transport   | bus | jet-ski | van | trike  |

