.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, lizard, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, parkour, lacrosse, badminton
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not the owner of the bird##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the owner of the lizard is not the person who's sport is badminton##6
6. the person who's sport is parkour is not the owner of the turtle##6
7. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | lizard | bird        | mouse  | turtle     |
| Sport   | ice-hockey     | badminton | parkour | lacrosse |

