.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, gardening, video-games, dancing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, blues, reggae, classical
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
2. the fan blues is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
3. the fan reggae is not the person who's hobby is video-games##6
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the fan classical and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the fan blues is between the fan d&b and the person who's hobby is cooking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | gardening    | cooking | dancing |
| Music-Genre   | d&b         | blues | classical   | reggae     |

