.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, nectarine, cauliflower, kale
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, scooter, jet-ski
1. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
2. the person eating kale is not the person driving the train##6
3. the person driving the ship is the person eating kale##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
5. the person driving the scooter is not the person eating kale##6
6. the person eating nectarine is not the person driving the train##6
7. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person eating nectarine##5
8. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | peas  | cauliflower | nectarine | kale |
| Transport   | scooter | train     | jet-ski     | ship    |

