.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, mango, radish, apple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, superhero, sports, spy
1. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating mango is not the person watching superhero movies##6
3. the person eating pepper is the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5
5. the person eating pepper is between the person eating mango and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | apple | mango      | pepper | radish   |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | sports | spy   | musical |

