3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | tea    | mirinda | 7up | soy-milk         |
| Sport      | parkour | snowboarding | ice-hockey          | volleyball |

