1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the owner of the cat is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rabbit##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | reading | filmmaking | baking |
| Pet     | horse  | rabbit      | turtle  | cat       |

