.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, lemonade, hot-chocolate
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, bus, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the bike is not the person drinking tea##6
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
6. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | tea | fanta | hot-chocolate      | lemonade   |
| Transport   | tram  | boat   | bus | bike |

 